All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArgsInformation
    ArgsInformation Object that stores values of the Information required to be passed into the ArgsValidator Object.
    ArgsValidator
    ArgsValidator Object that verifies if a list of Strings are the valid arguments based on the Map of Argument Informations it is constructed with.
    Command
    Interface for Commands that would be executed by the REPL.
    CSVParser
    Parser responsisble for reading the CSV File and ensuring the file is properly formatted according to standards set.
    LineConverter<T>
    Interface for anonymnous methods that takes in a String and returns a generic type T.
    Main
    The Main class of our project.
    MockCSV
    MockCSV Command Object for executing the "mock csv" command.
    MockPerson
    MockPerson Object for representing a MockPerson in the "mock csv" command.
    NaiveNeighbors
    Naive Neighbors Command Object for executing the "naive_neighbors ..." command.
    NaiveRadius
    Naive Radius Command Object for executing the "naive_radius ..." command.
    REPLRunner
    REPLRunner that initiates the REPL Loop until being termianted.
    Star
    The Stars Object that stores the information from the CSV File.
    StarsUtilities
    Interface for the Utilities Functions in the star package.
    StringValFunctions
    Interface that stores some general StringValidations to be used by other Objects.
    StringValidation
    Interface for anonymnous methods that takes in a String and returns a Boolean.
    UpdateStarFile
    Stars Command Object for executing the "stars filepath" command.
